{"tid":885052,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"生食豬肉！女子全身爬滿「上百寄生蟲」　X光照嚇死網友","createTime":"2018-11-01T05:22:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-07T03:36:18.000Z","uid":130626,"like":383,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":103,"replies":[{"pid":"94726eaa9c43587b78ff605f13561e4199c5ea04","tid":885052,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T05:22:08.000Z","msg":"食用沒煮熟殺菌的食物，有可能因此感染寄生蟲！泰國一名女子因為生食豬肉，結果身體被數百隻絛蟲寄生，透過X光照片可以看到，絛蟲遍佈她的全身，連雙腿都沒能倖免，畫面相當驚悚。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/10/31/1618114-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F10%2F31%2F1618114-XXL.jpg&h=09968c80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲女子雙腿中的密集白點，正是豬肉絛蟲。（圖／翻攝自臉書）<br />\n<br />\n有網友3日在臉書分享一張X光照片，表示一名女子因為生食豬肉，導致身體被寄生蟲感染，只見X光照片中，女子全身、雙腳遍佈了密密麻麻的白色點點，而這些白點正是豬肉絛蟲。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/10/31/1618115-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F10%2F31%2F1618115-XXL.jpg&h=9233c0ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲女子生食豬肉，導致寄生蟲爬滿全身。（圖／翻攝自臉書）<br />\n<br />\n據了解，這名女子已就醫接受治療，目前先服藥除掉一部分的寄生蟲，之後會再進行手術徹底清除。而X光照片曝光後，不少人看了狂起雞皮疙瘩，直呼「密集恐懼症慎入」、「好想吐」、「覺得全身都癢起來了&hellip;」"},{"pid":"7a4a50af9f106cbb3d4a82985618086418f38cc5","tid":885052,"uid":29689,"like":1226,"dislike":7,"score":1219,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T05:24:52.000Z","msg":"呢啲就高清大圖dllm"},{"pid":"46266f3122e748b71c6602332b8123f7047909eb","tid":885052,"uid":195169,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T05:25:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d168740ea1b5b5b4a8bab74f808bf2282248e38c","tid":885052,"uid":49978,"like":150,"dislike":1,"score":149,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T05:25:57.000Z","msg":"響個西爬出離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2db2ff2ab7a2c497029345dacbd88c974d0dc5e","tid":88