3a4","tid":885052,"uid":51532,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T08:04:02.000Z","msg":"食包花塔餅也事都無啦，郁D就驚！"},{"pid":"ee684e6fba7fe5f9673d489cf91645e98c83b678","tid":885052,"uid":22913,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T08:07:51.000Z","msg":"以為睇緊伊藤潤二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37530a818713f5aa7e2bb9acb114bbe7c9981101","tid":885052,"uid":40052,"like":34,"dislike":2,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T08:10:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 周圍生<br />\n<br />\n感染豬肉絛蟲成蟲，人體會面黃肌瘦，無力等。<br />\n感染囊蚴，如果囊是在腦，人會出現癲癇，如果數量過多，會死亡。如果囊蚴寄生在眼球，會出現失明<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一般情況下，豬在吃了有絛蟲卵的食物後，絛蟲卵在豬體內胃酸和酶的作用下開始孵化，生出六鉤蚴（hexacanth）。六鉤蚴接著進入豬的循環系統，最終在肌肉組織、腦組織等地方停留，發育成囊尾蚴，並被豬組織包圍形成一個囊（cyst）。當人吃了未煮熟的有絛蟲囊尾蚴的豬肉（通稱「米心肉」）後感染，囊尾蚴在人體小腸發育成豬肉絛蟲成蟲，頭節掛在小腸壁以吸取營養和並分生出節片以繁殖後代。"},{"pid":"7b1e3ca5861fa1d7b6665738503cb6d5fabbbd11","tid":885052,"uid":155197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6aba915c3aea5f605311014c037e817e4e86b7ac","tid":885052,"uid":34241,"like":257,"dislike":3,"score":254,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T05:26:24.000Z","msg":"今次要用千鳥先救得返"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T08:12:09.000Z","msg":"雷切勁d先救到"},{"pid":"a5818c883cfd4a0e0810125dcda9f0444d5e0256","tid":885052,"uid":55179,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T08:14:03.000Z","msg":"屌你老母癡撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"154423a72717a948c9101077ddadda0a9fc